{"word":"Timbrel","slug":"timbrel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Timbrel</b> Called also Tabret, an instrument of music of the tambourine sort.<br/> Used by Miriam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=20'>Exo 15:20</a><br/> Used by Jephthah's daughter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=34'>Jdg 11:34</a><br/> Used in religious service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=5'>2Sa 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=13&verse=8'>1Ch 13:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=25'>Psa 68:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=2'>Psa 81:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=149&verse=3'>Psa 149:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=150&verse=4'>Psa 150:4</a><br/> Used in dances<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=21&verse=12'>Job 21:12</a><br/><a href='S:Music, Instruments of'>Music, Instruments of</a>"}]}